TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
/* Formatted on 4/7/2010 3:30:26 PM (QP5 v5.115.810.9015) */ /* d-claim-legacy-xref NON-Equine */
SELECT clm_no_cd, clm_no_cd_prev, feature_number, party_inst_ebi_no, feature_catg_cd, src_sys_cd, clm_ebi_txt, clm_feat_ebi_txt, unvrfy_pol_ind, claimant_ebi_text, clm_inst_ebi_no, clm_feat_inst_ebi_no, edw_busn_dt, finance_reported_previous_ind, cc_feature_number FROM (SELECT DISTINCT clm_no_cd, LAG (clm_no_cd, 1) OVER (ORDER BY clm_no_cd) AS clm_no_cd_prev, --SUBSTR (clm_feat_order_no, -1) clm_feat_order_no, ROW_NUMBER () OVER ( PARTITION BY clm_no_cd, claimant_ebi_text, party_inst_ebi_no ORDER BY clm_feat_order_no ) feature_number, party_inst_ebi_no, feature_catg_cd, src_sys_cd, clm_ebi_txt, clm_feat_ebi_txt, unvrfy_pol_ind, claimant_ebi_text, clm_inst_ebi_no, clm_feat_inst_ebi_no, edw_busn_dt, finance_reported_previous_ind, clm_feat_order_no cc_feature_number FROM (SELECT vwta_claim.clm_no_cd, vwta_clm_feat.clm_feat_order_no, vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_inst_ebi_no, vwta_clm_feat.feature_catg_cd, vw_edw_trans.src_sys_cd, vwta_claim.clm_ebi_txt, vwta_clm_feat.clm_feat_ebi_txt, vwa_pol_term.unvrfy_pol_ind, vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_ebi_txt claimant_ebi_text, vwta_claim.clm_inst_ebi_no, vwta_clm_feat.clm_feat_inst_ebi_no, vwta_claim.edw_busn_dt, ROW_NUMBER () OVER ( PARTITION BY clm_no_cd, vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_ebi_txt || vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_inst_ebi_no, clm_feat_order_no ORDER BY clm_no_cd, vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_ebi_txt || vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_inst_ebi_no, clm_feat_order_no ASC, feature_catg_cd NULLS LAST, vw_edw_trans.source_process_ts DESC, vw_edw_trans.transaction_group_part_no DESC ) rn, vw_edw_trans.source_process_ts, vw_edw_trans.transaction_group_part_no, vw_edw_trans.finance_reported_previous_ind FROM vwta_claim, vwta_clm_feat, vwta_clm_feat_claimant, vw_edw_trans, vwa_pol_term, vwa_pol_risk_cvrg --adw.edw_process_control WHERE vwta_claim.claim_id = vwta_clm_feat.claim_id AND vwta_claim.edw_trans_id = vwta_clm_feat.edw_trans_id AND vwta_clm_feat.clm_feat_id = vwta_clm_feat_claimant.clm_feat_id AND vwta_clm_feat.edw_trans_id = vwta_clm_feat_claimant.edw_trans_id AND vwta_claim.edw_trans_id = vw_edw_trans.edw_trans_id AND vwta_clm_feat.coverage_rating_id = vwa_pol_risk_cvrg.coverage_rating_id AND vwa_pol_risk_cvrg.pol_term_id = vwa_pol_term.pol_term_id AND vwa_pol_risk_cvrg.edw_trans_id = vwa_pol_term.edw_trans_id --AND vwta_claim.edw_busn_dt = edw_process_control.edw_busn_dt --AND edw_process_control.active_ind = 1 AND vw_edw_trans.finance_reported_previous_ind = 0 AND vwa_pol_term.pol_symbol_cd <> 'AMP' ORDER BY clm_no_cd, vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_ebi_txt || vwta_clm_feat_claimant.party_inst_ebi_no, clm_feat_order_no ASC, feature_catg_cd NULLS LAST, party_inst_ebi_no ASC) WHERE rn = 1) WHERE feature_number BETWEEN 1 AND 9 ORDER BY clm_no_cd, clm_no_cd_prev NULLS FIRST, claimant_ebi_text, party_inst_ebi_no

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: iif((isnull(CLM_NO_CD) OR isnull(FEATURE_NUMBER) OR isnull(PARTY_INST_EBI_NO) OR isnull(FEATURE_CATG_CD) OR isnull(SRC_SYS_CD) OR isnull(UNVRFY_POL_IND)),0,1)
